OL,3,CMan, 19, left with life-changing
OL,4,Cinjuries after 'targeted' shooting
OL,6,FA 19-year-old man has been rushed to
OL,7,Fhospital with life-changing injuries
OL,8,Ffollowing a "targeted" shooting.
OL,10,FGreater Manchester Police (GMP) were
OL,11,Fcalled to Beswicke Royds Street in
OL,12,FRochdale at 3:20pm on Thursday, 5
OL,13,FMarch, following reports that shots
OL,14,Fhad been fired.
OL,16,FEmergency services discovered the
OL,17,Fteenager with a gunshot wound to his
OL,18,Fleg. He was taken to hospital where he
OL,19,Fremains in a serious but not life-
OL,20,Fthreatening condition, police say.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
