PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1772817083
OL,3,CMan, 19, left with life-changing
OL,4,Cinjuries after 'targeted' shooting
OL,6,FSuperintendent Lucy Smallwood said:
OL,7,F"Since first receiving the reports,
OL,8,Four officers were at the scene within
OL,9,Fminutes, and we are working quickly to
OL,10,Funderstand the circumstances
OL,11,Fsurrounding this incident.
OL,13,F"It is believed this was a targeted
OL,14,Fattack and there is no wider threat to
OL,15,Fthe public."
OL,17,F"This incident will undoubtedly cause
OL,18,Fconcern," Superintendent Smallwood
OL,19,Fadded. "Officers will remain in the
OL,20,Fcommunity to provide reassurance and
OL,21,Fmaintain a visible presence.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
