OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1772817083
OL,3,CMan, 19, left with life-changing
OL,4,Cinjuries after 'targeted' shooting
OL,6,F"If you have any concerns, please
OL,7,Fspeak to an officer."
OL,9,FNo arrests have been made, and an
OL,10,Furgent appeal for information has been
OL,11,Flaunched. Detectives are particularly
OL,12,Fkeen to speak with anyone who may have
OL,13,Fcaptured the incident on camera.
OL,15,FAnyone with information is urged to
OL,16,Fcontact police on 101, quoting log
OL,17,F2097 of 05/03/2026. Alternatively, you
OL,18,Fcan contact the independent charity
OL,19,FCrimestoppers anonymously on 0800 555
OL,20,F111.
